# Puchi Frontend

Puchi là nền tảng web học tiếng Việt. Frontend dùng **Next.js 16 (App Router) + React 19**.

## Tech Stack

| Thành phần | Công nghệ |
|------------|-----------|
| Framework | Next.js 16 (App Router) |
| UI | Tailwind CSS v4 + Shadcn UI (New York) |
| State | Zustand v5 |
| Auth | Supertokens (self-host, Email/Password + Google + Facebook + TikTok) |
| i18n | next-intl (9 ngôn ngữ) |
| Animation | Motion + Rive |
| Runtime | Bun |

## Scripts

```bash
bun install          # Cài dependencies
bun run dev          # Dev server
bun run build        # Build production
bun run lint         # ESLint
```

## Cấu trúc thư mục

```
src/
├── app/[locale]/     # Next.js App Router pages (i18n)
├── components/       # UI components (Shadcn + custom)
├── lib/              # Utilities, API clients
├── store/            # Zustand stores
├── hooks/            # Custom hooks
├── i18n/             # Translation config
├── services/         # API service layer
├── styles/           # Global styles
├── constants/        # Constants
└── types/            # TypeScript types
```

## CI/CD

- **CI**: GitHub Actions (`ci-cd.yml`) - Lint, Build Docker, Push GHCR
- **Docker**: Multi-stage build voi Bun, output `standalone`
- **Registry**: `ghcr.io/puchidemy/puchi-frontend`

## Kết noi Backend

- API qua Envoy Gateway tai `api.puchi.io.vn`
- Auth: Supertokens (da migrate tu Clerk)
